@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@token = your_token_here
@bookingId = 1

### Get All Bookings — Admin / Approver
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Booking Detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings/{{bookingId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Booking
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "vehicle_id": 1,
    "driver_id": 1,
    "requester_name": "Budi Hartono",
    "purpose": "Kunjungan lapangan ke site tambang",
    "destination": "Site Tambang Blok B, Morowali",
    "start_date": "2026-05-01 08:00:00",
    "end_date": "2026-05-02 08:00:00",
    "approver_level1_id": 2,
    "approver_level2_id": 3
}

### Approve Booking — Approver
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings/{{bookingId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Reject Booking — Approver (notes wajib)
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings/{{bookingId}}/reject
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "notes": "Kendaraan sedang dibutuhkan unit lain pada periode tersebut."
}

# =============================================================================
# EDGE CASES
# =============================================================================

### Create Booking — Validation Error (missing fields)
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "vehicle_id": 1
}

### Create Booking — Self-approval (approver_level1_id = admin id)
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "vehicle_id": 1,
    "driver_id": 1,
    "requester_name": "Test Self Approval",
    "purpose": "Test",
    "destination": "Test",
    "start_date": "2026-05-03 08:00:00",
    "end_date": "2026-05-04 08:00:00",
    "approver_level1_id": 1,
    "approver_level2_id": 3
}